title: User:NewSquidbeakSplatoon/Enperry Splat Dualies Demo
content:
The purpose of this page is to show other editors what Competitive Weapon pages are to look like from now on. (Specifically, the images.) The role of each Infobox shows its current status. Thank you for taking the time to look at this, and don't forget to Stay Fresh!

P.S. Please note that images for Splatoon (the first game in the series) will be using the icons from Splatnet, available in the gallery for the weapon. (on it's respective page)
